Dorothy Granger https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dorothy_Granger 0 Dorothy Karolyn Granger (November 21, 1912 – January 4, 1995) was an American actress best known for her roles in short subject comedies in Hollywood. She was also the stepmother of film maker and former record producer Anthony J. Hilder.
